{"tid":2028240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚耀宗：舉外國旗即勾結外部勢力 毀國家安全","createTime":"2020-05-21T17:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T07:54:21.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0cb283e9f1415fdd0d5e6ea0cba168f284d7fe","tid":2028240,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:00:40.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委譚耀宗接受傳媒查詢時指，人大晚上的預備會未有透露港版國安法的具體內容，但他稱，香港在過去數年發生很多挑戰和衝擊國家安全的例子，如污損國旗國徽、中央駐港機構被破壞和攻擊，並舉起外國的旗幟，認為是與外國勢力結合，破壞國家安全，有關行為都是《基本法》23條所不容許，指人大會議研究如何保護「一國兩制」和維護國家安全，再研究日後如何跟進，否認等同撕毀《基本法》。"},{"pid":"f827e3930c9e068f42399058357873aa9b02c314","tid":2028240,"uid":135277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"點解佢哋唔諗下點改善而喺不斷用手法令呢樣野唔再岀現"},{"pid":"778d646700e9b217c9bff1df3f75d0e6b8b6a06b","tid":2028240,"uid":2267,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"香港人：揸住外國護照即勾結外部勢力，毁国家安全"},{"pid":"19d6942aff15b8595cbbf6d87172974705d3b508","tid":2028240,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"持外國資產即為釣結外國勢力, 已犯國安法"},{"pid":"4b2b19db0d6591b64f658afa733b214d2647d455","tid":2028240,"uid":7078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRhPM6j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRhPM6j.gif&h=06fe1084&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b988f9789a8758bac2b8e1d03ed8ae1a7376722","tid":2028240,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T17:10:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中國最大外國勢力</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D5sFTW-UEAEzHv9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD5sFTW-UEAEzHv9.jpg&h=6437d18a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dv8pM4iUcAAK5GF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht